Package: CoseRo
Type: Package
Title: R Interface and Shiny Application for the COSERO Hydrological Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mathew", "Herrnegger",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mathew.herrnegger@boku.ac.at"),
    person("COSERO Development Team",
           role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Provides an R interface for the COSERO hydrological model,
    including automated model execution, fast output reading, an interactive
    Shiny visualization app, and a Sobol-based global sensitivity analysis
    framework. Users can run COSERO simulations programmatically or through
    a web GUI.
License: GPL (>= 3) | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
